#                 weaponized proof-of-concept.  Go=176 leader bump
#                 continuing Axis 121 (DNS / IETF RFC-1035 + DoT
#                 RFC-7858 + DoH RFC-8484 + DoQ RFC-9250 name-
#                 resolution protocol) at 2/0/0 via the canonical
#                 Go DNS library **github.com/miekg/dns**.
# ============================================================================
#
# UPSTREAM
